    <text x="150" y="150" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="13" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Profitable that year only (no persistence) — about 19%</text>
    <rect x="20" y="158" width="122" height="34" fill="#60a5fa"/>
    <text x="20" y="222" fill="#f87171" font-size="13" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Unprofitable — about 80%</text>
    <rect x="20" y="230" width="512" height="34" fill="#f87171"/>
    </svg>
  <p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">※ Figures are rounded approximations from Barber, Lee, Liu, and Odean's (2014) analysis of individual day traders on the Taiwan Stock Exchange. The top bar (under 1%) is drawn thicker than its true proportion for legibility.</p>
  </div>
